#!/usr/bin/python3
"""Production Busdriver draft parser and state-check dispatcher.

Pattern:
  lock acquire -> gate preflight -> guarded agent command -> gate postflight -> lock release -> report

Production Pi/OpenCode mutation dispatch is policy-blocked until trusted OS
containment and credential brokering exist. Non-installed runpy fixtures retain
adapter contract coverage; no CLI or environment switch enables that seam.
"""

